7. Create all /lib/db/queries/*.ts files
8. Create seed files (assets, 3D components, templates)
9. Create /scripts/setup.ts
10. Run setup: npx tsx scripts/setup.ts
11. Replace all SQLite imports in API routes
12. Update all tool execution functions (async)
13. Create /lib/storage/index.ts (local/cloud media)
14. Create /app/projects/page.tsx (project browser)
15. Update package.json scripts
16. Test local mode end-to-end
17. Test cloud mode with Neon (create free account, get URL)
18. Verify migrations run clean on fresh Neon DB

